ata-recommend-id=\"image://f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"675\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A Joy-Con 2.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A Joy-Con 2.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A Joy-Con 2.\" data-chomp-id=\"f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"675\" data-alt=\"A Joy-Con 2.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Nintendo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f2cd769736b8d8fe3580fb0156c808b6\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"675\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A Joy-Con 2.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eI finally got to play the \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-c-button-animal-crossing-zelda-friend-codes-1851775334\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-c-button-animal-crossing-zelda-friend-codes-1851775334\"\u003eSwitch 2\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. It happened as part of a demo here at PAX East, and though my time with the system was brief (and I wasn’t even allowed to look at the console itself as it was hidden beneath a demo station), it did give me a chance to play around with one of the features I was most curious about: the mouse controls. I don’t typically play games on my PC, and when I do, I don’t often use my mouse if I can help it. However, I’m always interested in control methods that can bridge the gap between styles of play we typically associate with other platforms. PlayStation’s touch pads have given console players a trackpad equivalent, for instance, so naturally, someone needed to build a proper mouse into a console controller at some point. I found a surprisingly convincing tech demo for the Switch 2’s mouse controls in \u003cem\u003eBravely Default Flying Fairy HD Remaster\u003c/em\u003e. The specific playing experience I had wasn’t ideal, but it did sell me on the tech. - Kenneth Shepard \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-mouse-controls-joycon-bravely-default-1851779935\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-mouse-controls-joycon-bravely-default-1851779935\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"33fa57ab17635df172d206c84ff08cbb\" data-recommend-id=\"image://33fa57ab17635df172d206c84ff08cbb\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A Nintendo Switch 2 with a brick dropped on it.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u0